---
description: Preserve onboarding routing and completion invariants
globs: src/{middleware.ts,auth.ts,app/onboarding/**/*.{ts,tsx}}
alwaysApply: false
---

# Onboarding Invariants

- Unauthenticated users are redirected to `/login` for protected routes.
- Authenticated users with incomplete onboarding are redirected to `/onboarding`.
- Users with completed onboarding should not remain on `/login` or `/onboarding`.
- The onboarding completion action must:
  - Persist profile metrics and lifestyle data.
  - Mark onboarding as completed in the user record.
  - Synchronize session state so middleware reflects the new completion flag.
